snippet.title: This is Bravest Chicken
snippet.description:
Bravest Chicken is an upcoming precision platformer that mixes Flappy Bird jumping with high stakes gameplay of Jump King.

You can wishlist "Bravest Chicken" on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2359270/Bravest_Chicken/

Play the prototype on itch.io: https://frajdagames.itch.io/bravest-chicken

Twitter: https://twitter.com/FrajdaGames
itch.io: https://frajdagames.itch.io
